Package models

Class GymMerch

java.lang.Object
models.GymMerch
public class GymMerch extends Object
GymMerch class representing gym merchandise details in the system. Fields correspond to the GymMerch table in the database. Fields: - merchID: Unique identifier for the merchandise - merchName: Name of the merchandise - merchType: Type of the merchandise - merchPrice: Price of the merchandise - quantityInStock: Quantity of the merchandise in stock Author: Abiodun Magret Oyedele Date: 2025-12-06
